Create a modern, high-converting ecommerce grocery website for a local store named "New Sarthak Bazar".

Location: Robertsganj, Uttar Pradesh, India.

The website should look professional, fast, and mobile-friendly. The design should be clean, modern, and optimized for conversions.

Main Features:

1. Homepage
- Attractive hero banner with grocery products.
- Store tagline: "Fresh Groceries at Best Price".
- Quick categories section (Rice, Oil, Snacks, Daily Essentials, Beverages, Household Items).
- Featured products section.
- Best deals and discounts banner.
- Customer reviews section.
- Call and WhatsApp quick buttons.

2. Product Catalog
- Product grid with images, price, discount, rating.
- Categories filter.
- Search bar.
- Add to cart button.

3. Product Page
- Large product image.
- Price and discount.
- Quantity selector.
- Add to cart / Buy now.
- Product description.
- Customer reviews.

4. Shopping Cart
- List of added products.
- Quantity update.
- Remove items.
- Total price calculation.

5. Checkout Page
- Customer name
- Phone number
- Address
- Payment options:
   - Cash on Delivery
   - UPI
   - Online payment

6. Order Management
- Order confirmation page.
- Order tracking status.

7. Return & Refund System
- Return request form.
- Refund policy page.
- Easy product return option.

8. Extra Features
- WhatsApp order button.
- Google Maps location.
- Contact page with phone number.
- Customer login/signup.
- Admin dashboard to add products and manage orders.

Design Style:
- Colors: Red, White, and Yellow (grocery style).
- Clean UI with product shelves look.
- Mobile-first responsive design.

Goal:
Increase local grocery orders and allow customers to easily browse products, order, and request returns online.
